latestPosts.caption:
💥 Powder can make or break your makeup! 💥

Have always been a fan of the Huda Beauty powders  however couldn't resist buying the Makeup by Mario Loose Powder ✨️

👁️ Huda takes the lead for under-eyes — it blurs beautifully without settling into fine lines 🙌
✨ Mario wasn't the best for my under eye lines — however after using it a few times I do feel it would be better suited for the oily skin girls😃 Also love the colors they have introduced for deeper skintones. 

Tell me your favorite ??💬👇

🎀 Lashes- Twiggy @thenaristudio
